title: *PATREON PREVIEW* 1am In Midtown Pt. II with Adam Pally and Dan Levy
description:
Luxury podding and luxury podcasters never sleep. The boyz are back with Adam Pally and Dan Levy of NBC’s upcoming sitcom “Indebted,” which premieres tonight at 9:30 PM EST. Even as the witching hour approaches, no stone is left unturned: How can TF make the jump to Hollywood? What’s it like navigating full-frontal male nudity? Can a guest star really move the needle? Are Jimmy and Larry finally ready to officially endorse a presidential candidate? Lock in with The Only Podcast That Matters™ for another Patreon-exclusive throwdown.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
